or', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/294649/', '', 'Imatinib, Dabrafenib, Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Pexidartinib, Tepotinib, Fedratinib, Avapritinib, Larotrectinib, Selumetinib, Cobimetinib, More', 'Alvimopan, Sorbitol, Tegaserod, Bisacodyl, Lactulose, Methylnaltrexone, Lactitol, Sodium sulfate, Linaclotide, Plecanatide, Lubiprostone, More', 1767369485);
